rk-zwierzecy">Folwark zwierzęcy</a></div><a class="quote-tile__link" href="https://lubimyczytac.pl/cytat/176" title="Zobacz więcej" aria-label="Zobacz więcej"><i class="icon icon-arrow-right"></i></a><div class="quote-tile__buttons"><span class="quote-tile__button quote-tile__button--favorites"><span class="icon icon-icon-menu-21-ulubieniAutorzy"></span><span>1003</span> osoby&nbsp;to&nbsp;lubią </span><button class="quote-tile__button quote-tile__button--add" data-url="quote/addToFavorities"><i class="icon icon-heart"></i>Dodaj do ulubionych</button><button class="quote-tile__button quote-tile__button--remove" data-url="quote/removeFromFavorities"><i class="icon icon-heart-fill"></i>Usuń z ulubionych</button></div></article></li></ul><a class="favorite-quotes__cta" href="https://lubimyczytac.pl/cytaty">Więcej cytatów</a></div></div></section><div class="calendar carousel carousel--custom"><div class="calendar__title"><h2> Kalendarium literackie</h2><div class="calendar__date"><input class="calendar__input" type="date" value="2023-11-22" min="2023-01-01" max="2023-12-31" data-placeholder="22 listopada"><button class="calendar__button calendar__button--datepicker"><i class="calendar__icon icon-calendar"></i></button><button class="calendar__button calendar__button--prev"><i class="calendar__icon icon-chevron-left"></i></button><button class="calendar__button calendar__button--next"><i class="calendar__icon icon-chevron-right"></i></button></div></div><div class="carousel__slider" data-per-view="4" data-lazy-el="20" data-lazy-url="fetchLiteraryCalendar"><div class="carousel__wrapper"><div class="carousel__slide"><a class="calendar__tile" href="https://lubimyczytac.pl/autor/6173/krystyna-siesicka" title="Idź na stronę autora Krystyna Siesicka"><div class="calendar__intro"> Tego dnia urodziła się </div><div class="calendar__author"> Krystyna Siesicka </div><div class="calendar__anniversary calendar__anniversary--birth"> 95. rocznica urodzin </div><img class="calendar__b